Text: RE OASIS Site Feedback oasissecuretransmissionnewreservati onaspPST Were having intermittent problems related to accepting reservations via our website We are looking into the cause of the problem and are working to have it resolved as soon as possible As the nature of the problems appears to be intermittent please try to resubmit your reservation request Michael H Mraz IS Manager Transmission Systems Pinnacle West Capital Corporation PO Box Phoenix AZ Ph Fx Original Message From Salisbury Holden mailto Sent Monday June AM To Subject OASIS Site Feedback oasissecuretransmissionnewreservationasp If you have discovered a bug with the OASIS web site please include as much information about what you were trying to do and the error message returned I cannot purchase any daily transmission on the AZPS oasis site Error is below An error occurred in processing this page Please contact the servers administrator if this problem persists Number Source CRequestGetRecords Description Invalid procedure call or argument Extended Information TemplateParseCRequestGetRecords failed Please let me know what I can do
